-- UniCredit May Name Both Nicastro and Ermotti to GM Positions, MF Reports
-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 2010-10-14T06:37:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/unicredit-may-name-both-nicastro-and-ermotti-to-gm-positions-mf-reports.html
UniCredit SpA  Chief Executive
Officer  Federico Ghizzoni  yesterday offered deputies  Roberto Nicastro  and  Sergio Ermotti  general manager positions, newspaper
MF reported, without saying where it got the information.  Nicastro would be responsible for commercial banking, while
Ermotti would be in charge of corporate and investment banking,
according to the Italian newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Armorel Kenna  in Milan at 
 akenna@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net  